tourBios.carHigh: 2015: Finished T13 at the Florida Qualifying Tournament, with rounds of 69-72-63-69. Played 12 events, with eight made cuts and three top 25s. At the SIGA Dakota Dunes Open, was T4 at the turn. A disastrous Saturday-round 76 moved him down the leaderboard to T155. Recoved nicely Sunday with a final-round 67 and a T19 finish...Second top 25 (T16) came at the Staal Foundation Open in Thunder Bay...Four weeks later, posted his best finish, a T5, at the National Capital Open capitalizing on four under-par rounds punctuated by matching weekend 65s at Hylands GC.
tourBios.personal: Worked as a high school teacher...Dream foursome would include Bobby Jones, Franklin D. Roosevelt and his dad...Braves, Cardinals, Falcons and Penguins fan...Hopes to play Augusta National someday...Always uses a numbered ball that correlates to the round of the tournament...Twitter account is @wade_binfield.

dyn.dynBios: Played against NBA player Dwight Howard.
dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the Mackenzie Tour-PGA T was T5th in 2015 at the National Capital Open to Support Our Troops.
dyn.dynStats: He ranks T56th in Scoring Average (Actual) on the Mackenzie Tour-PGA TOUR Canada.
